  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large cazuela over medium heat.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and saute for 1 minute.",
    "Add the blanched and seasoned namul and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped fresh basil and mint and stir well.",
    "Add the thinly sliced serrano ham and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional fresh herbs if desired."
